# Simple Sigma Detection Rules
# Rule: T1110 - Failed Logon Attempts (Brute Force)
# Author: Philip Zangara
# MITRE ATT&CK: T1110 - Brute Force
# Generated from Sigma rule using sigma-cli with splunk_windows pipeline
# Note: Threshold logic applied in SPL - Sigma pipe syntax deprecated in pySigma
# Usage: Paste into Splunk search bar or save as a saved search

EventCode=4625 LogName="Security"
| stats count by src_ip, user 
| where count > 5